snippet.title: When Pigs Fly - Chicken Passenger service from Alexander Farms to Lake Varden
snippet.description:
A rare When Pigs Fly video with no crashes!

I built this big amphibious flying boat and really loved they way it flew, so I loaded up 20 chickens and took a short flight from Alexander Farms to Lake Varden.  I flew through the drag race course along the way as well.

When Pigs Fly is available here:
http://gamejolt.com/games/when-pigs-fly/39898

Follow me on Twitter @Gaudino Games

Check out my website: www.gaudinogames.com
